@anahad bhau. Aapla manapasoon aabhar ki tumhi majhi barobari malikjee sarkhya gurun barobar kelat. 

Tumchya sarkhya film rasikan kadun jevha don shabd aabharache vachayla milte tevha mala duppat sfurti milte.

Bhau asech don shabd vyakt karat raha ani mala sfurti det raha. Tumcha janma bhar aabhari rahen.
